Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
