Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过了 我是超越变革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda不会交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 引导人类的是我
