Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用自己的意志 创造未来
