Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你…不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇…
