Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去托勒密会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹剩余不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的生命 会消失
