Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那Gundam 连我们都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷杰尼·雷杰塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯种变革者的脑量子波 和Twin Drive连动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯度提高的GN粒子 会扩张人们的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成完全进化了吗 刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是…真正的变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这恶心的感觉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人把哥哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那家伙的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得一杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子就是老子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别东张西望 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看着玛丽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么不可思议的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音直接在脑中响起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 毕利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明知你的心意 却利用了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了实现永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决心为此而战的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是声音 比利斯中尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算一直恨你 报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也一定不会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么将亲生父亲 将上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也背叛了军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他扰乱了永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校不是会做那种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 他对母亲见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 不试图彼此理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 那个人没对我说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是借口 还是谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没试图理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我杀了他 亲手杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要他理解你 你为何不去理解上校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校一定是为你着想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为何当时什么也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说的话 谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说的话
